---
/**
 * Home Page - YAML-Driven Configuration
 *
 * This page is now powered by YAML configuration from src/data/pages/home.yaml
 * All content, layout, and component ordering is controlled through that YAML file.
 *
 * To customize this page:
 * 1. Edit src/data/pages/home.yaml
 * 2. Add/remove/reorder components in the YAML file
 * 3. Modify component configurations and copy
